message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD. The paper discusses a natural language system that uses interactive questioning to improve classification accuracy, which is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. Specifically, cs.CL (Computation and Language) deals with natural language processing, while cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are both relevant due to the use of machine learning techniques. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and data management (cs.SD) in terms of the system's decision-making process.
